node.text:
As you all kept asking me, here is finally my little make up tutorial and my first IGTV video 😌 it’s a little fast as I tried to include everything, but don’t make it too long... so if there are any questions feel free to comment below. 
And all the exact products tagged here, so you can know exactly what I used. Hope you like it and stay safe 😘 
1. Concealer Double wear instant fix Estée Lauder 
2. Contour stick benefit Hoola
3. Studio fix powder Mac
4. Highlighter hyper glow Mac
5. Bronzer mineralize skin finish Mac
6. Lip pencil Mac colour Spice (my fav)
7. Eyebrow mascara Benefit
8. Eyeshadow pure envy Estée Lauder colour Wicked Peach
9. Eyeshadow palette Starry eyes Charlotte tilbury 
10. Eyeliner Benefit
11. Mascara Marc Jacobs
